          "musical_style": "南梆子",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "我心中只把那余洪来恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "南梆子",
          "musical_style": "南梆子",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "大不该害儿夫这样的苦情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖小开门〗，〖牌子〗。刘金定画符，仗剑烧符。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "南梆子",
          "musical_style": "南梆子",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "望尊神你速速降临宋营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天灵灵地灵灵，药王神何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王引小鬼同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "正在洞中要过瘾，"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听小鬼报一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "她因她丈夫得病，特地请吾师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "她的法谕我是怎敢不尊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见了那仙姑说分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃药王是也。正在洞中要开灯过瘾，忽然小鬼报道，宋营刘金定有法谕相召，"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要叫吾神与他丈夫治病，来此已是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小鬼！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小鬼允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带路一同进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，仙姑请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙姑见召，有何法谕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊神有所不知：只因我丈夫高俊保身染重病，百药不能见效，特请尊神前来替"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们治上一治。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此，但不知此病是因何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因番营来了一将名唤余洪，乃是一个妖道。是我丈夫在两军阵前与他交战，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不知道他用什么宝贝，将我丈夫打下马来。是奴家杀上前去，将我丈夫救回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁知道他就病啦！也曾用药医治，总不见效。因此特请尊神到来，给我们看"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看，务要速速的治好了他才好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。仙姑但放宽心，不是小神夸口，管保是手到病除，比一把抓还要灵"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "应些呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就请尊神医治。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待吾神先来看脉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此病本是打从惊吓而起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么要得请尊神开了药方子罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不须开方。吾带得有仙药在此，待吾神与你配合好了，管保一剂定要痊愈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王捶小鬼背。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龟背三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王抓小鬼头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兔脑丸二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王摸小鬼虎皮裙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鳖甲二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王抓小鬼裤裆。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海狗肾二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王揉小鬼腹。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大腹皮二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王打小鬼腿。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "牛膝三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王握小鬼手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸡爪黄连二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王踩小鬼脚。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皂角三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王摸小鬼屁股。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蟾酥锭二钱。得啦，你身上的东西全取完啦。你起开了罢。待我自己身上再取"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几样贵重药材。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王揉眼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙眼二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王扑胸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "川芎三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王按心。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莲心三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王抓左胁。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伏龙肝三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王抓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆南星二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王掠须。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙须草三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王摸足骨。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎胫骨三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王摇手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "佛手二钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王弹指。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "穿山甲三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王做屙屎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使君子三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王摸小便。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸡头米三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王蹲做溺。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "童便三钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好啦好啦这一剂，比仙丹还要灵的多。管保吃下去就好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哎，这么一大碗，他如何能够喝得下去呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "药虽多不要一起吃。分两次吃也可以呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他还说最怕吃药。一闻药味，他就呛出来了啦。还要想个法子才好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有法子。用过山龙来吃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么叫做过山龙吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个过山龙，是你把这一碗药拿过来吃上一口，对着他的嘴一点一点的往里送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他自然就不能喷出来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们知道啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这还有一个名堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫做二仙传道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾神告过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这一碗灵药甚贵重，"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天上难找地下难寻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "吾急速回去再开灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "药王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我回去吸我那半口鸦片烟去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（药王下，小鬼随下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里将药碗拿在手，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫将军且醒来细听从头："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定对高俊保面口送药。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "果然是一滴滴下了咽喉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定以口送药。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一霎时度下了十二重楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定以口送药。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又听得他腹内鸣好似水流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这药已经吃下去啦。但不知灵验不灵验？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得人把话讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高俊保看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一霎时只觉得遍体清凉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高俊保三笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再与娘子说端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓娘子，但不知你用什么灵药医治于我，这病体竟自痊愈了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军是你不知么？看看你的病症十分沉重，是奴情急无奈，特请药王老爷降下"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凡尘，与我开方医治，所以这个病才好的这么快。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此，多谢娘子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "躬身施礼把话讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多蒙你作法请药王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "定然一命丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若非灵药治我恙"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若非灵药治我恙"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为你病症我挂心上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妇恩爱也应当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今病体已愈，定要与那妖道见一高下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军不必着急，歇兵三日，妾身定要灭却妖道，与将军报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢娘子。请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高俊保、刘金定同下。〖牌子〗。）"
        }
